#: ../../user/templates/windows/qubes-windows.rst:6
#: 9ee87de4b0b04914aefe6f5db3cf8005
msgid ""
"You can install Windows just like any other OS as an :doc:`HVM </user"
"/advanced-topics/standalones-and-hvms>`, if you just want something "
"simple and you can live without some features. This works for Windows XP,"
" 7, 8, 8.1, 10, and 11."
