#: 20d61434e38d45d4962647b0bc9f0cb5
msgid ""
"Please keep in mind that Qubes Windows Tools are not supported on Windows"
" XP. Windows 8.1 may work comparable to Windows 10, but this has not been"
" tested, as this system is no longer supported and probably has no "
"significance anymore."
msgstr ""

